    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Activities and precautions designed to avoid an outbreak of fire, reduce the potential for fire to spread, and to safeguard persons, property, wildlife, and flora in the event of fire.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
